CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 11, 1956, pg. A15, reads: "Social Interlude...at intermission was enjoyed by this group. in foreground are Mrs. Lewis (Bud) Ulen of Harrisburg; John Lloyd and Hugo Hyde, Philadelphia; Mrs. William Grasty and Mr. Grasty, Braddock; Mrs. John Lloyd, Philadelphia, and Mrs, Wilson Primas of Harrisburg, with back to camera."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Mrs. Wilson Primas facing away, Mrs. Lewis (Bud) Ulen, John Lloyd, Hugo Hyde, Mrs. Gratsy, William Gratsy, and Mrs. Lloyd, standing in ballroom of Penn-Sheraton Hotel, for FROGS formal
